trans-unit.source: A literal expression stores the code of an expression as a literal code fragment.
trans-unit.target: 常值運算式會將運算式的程式碼儲存為常值的程式碼片段。

trans-unit.source: The CodeDOM does not translate literal code fragments.
trans-unit.target: CodeDOM 不會轉譯常值的程式碼片段。

trans-unit.source: Literal code fragments are stored and output just as they are.
trans-unit.target: 常值的程式碼片段會儲存，並輸出就如同它們。

trans-unit.source: CodeDOM objects that contain literal code are provided so developers can encapsulate code that is already in the target language.
trans-unit.target: CodeDOM 物件，其中包含常值的程式碼被為了讓開發人員可以將封裝已在目標語言的程式碼。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression.Value%2A> property contains the literal code for this snippet expression.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression.Value%2A>屬性包含這個程式碼片段運算式常值的程式碼。</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression"></xref> class using the specified literal expression.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression"></xref>類別使用指定的常值運算式。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the literal string of code.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定常值字串的程式碼。

trans-unit.source: This can contain code or comments.
trans-unit.target: 這可以包含程式碼註解。
